  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Quota Application for Green Card to Reimmigrate to USA",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa, who fled the country amid public protests demanding his resignation, is reportedly awaiting an American green card to return to the United States and settle there with his wife and son.",
        "As his wife Ayoma Rajapaksa is a US citizen, Rajapaksa's lawyers in the US started the application for a green card last month, according to top sources.",
        "Now his lawyers in Colombo are said to be taking it forward by submitting additional documents.",
        "It has been reported that the former president has canceled his initial plan to stay in Thailand until November and will return to Sri Lanka on August 25."
      ],
